{"tid":2436633,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"麥長青簽亞視一年主持拳賽 等曾志偉召喚回巢","createTime":"2021-03-07T09:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T13:30:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d43c9916e99a3e2786a3716a88d4154722d07c24","tid":2436633,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:38:27.000Z","msg":"麥長青（麥包）於2016年12月離開効力29年的無綫，之後返大陸搵錢，亦曾到ViuTV主持旅遊節目，今日他以自由身為亞視拳賽節目擔任主持，並聯同6位亞姐、劉永、黃夏蕙、陳惠敏和雪梨等人出席節目活動。<br />\n<br />\n麥包與友人合資的飲食店生意受疫情影響生意，他表示已找到對象、蝕住轉手，暫時不會搞生意，自己暫時仍然有做網上直播賣貨；而麥包的演藝事業則不停，下星期到深圳拍劇，暫不透露詳情，只表示演員都是熟悉都舊同事，入境後需強制隔離21天。自言仍會專注演藝事業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210307/HLQGSZGGGJEOZDAILP3RMAYGT4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210307%2FHLQGSZGGGJEOZDAILP3RMAYGT4%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=98d81807\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210307%2FHLQGSZGGGJEOZDAILP3RMAYGT4%2F&h=20b19049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210307/HLQGSZGGGJEOZDAILP3RMAYGT4/</a>"},{"pid":"c37074f386bf4aeb96d8ed9bb758b9b1fe5c04fb","tid":2436633,"uid":322388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZHuMbgY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZHuMbgY.gif&h=28921491&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1d1f2ab9faedfdfc150127509c4f277bbef6347","tid":2436633,"uid":84926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c37074f386bf4aeb96d8ed9bb758b9b1fe5c04fb","tid":2436633,"uid":322388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZHuMbgY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZHuMbgY.gif&h=28921491&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:43:49.000Z","msg":"呢個乜野事<im